solution.text:
Male reproductive system:
 
Gonads Testes (1 pair)
Accessory ducts Rete testis, vasa efferentia, epididymis, vas deferens
External genitalia Penis
Glands Seminal vesicles (pair), prostate gland (one), bulbourethral glands (pair)




Female reproductive system
 
Gonads Ovaries (1 pair)
Accessory ducts Oviducts (fallopian tubes), uterus, vagina
External genitalia Mons pubis, labia majora, Labia minora, hymen, clitoris
